        {
            "title": "豆腐渣？︱南昌屋苑樓頂磚牆遭吹散  石塊壓爛多輛汽車",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"江西南昌有屋苑的頂層「炮樓」被大風吹散。荔枝新聞\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a48554248c83391bb0746ddc8af317c2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041611321718618.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">江西南昌有屋苑的頂層「炮樓」被大風吹散。荔枝新聞</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>內地日前多地遭遇極端大風吹襲，江西南昌有屋苑的頂樓圍牆，竟然應風崩塌，碩大磚塊被「吹散」跌落街，將多輛泊在樓下汽車壓毀幸無傷人。屋民質疑涉及偷工減料豆腐渣工作，發展商辯稱是設計缺陷。當地住建局指已介入，正待專家鑑定。\n\n</p><h2>住建局：等待專家鑑定</h2>\n<p>據荔枝新聞報道，南昌屋苑保利天匯一期14日有一幢住宅頂層的「炮樓（凸出屋面的小建築）」，在大風吹襲之下，居然應聲「散架」，整幅牆倒塌，部份石塊跌落數十樓下，將泊在大廈周邊的多輛汽車壓毀，幸無人受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉事大樓下的多輛汽車被吹落的石塊擊毀。時速新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0d8c2717f118ff98eeb552241a7d9bd/2025-04/25623.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事大樓下的多輛汽車被吹落的石塊擊毀。時速新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉事大樓下的多輛汽車被吹落的石塊擊毀。時速新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a72aeda3702dcddd4f7a3709c664656/2025-04/51526.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事大樓下的多輛汽車被吹落的石塊擊毀。時速新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"涉事大樓下的多輛汽車被吹落的石塊擊毀。時速新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ca9bd1423c2e315bdb9bcdce507f57a/2025-04/526526_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事大樓下的多輛汽車被吹落的石塊擊毀。時速新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"大廈外牆部份亦被吹毀。抖音@南昌保利天滙天坑\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/91ada4a842cc5ddaa265e511a924e513/2025-04/001_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大廈外牆部份亦被吹毀。抖音@南昌保利天滙天坑\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江西南昌有屋苑的頂層「炮樓」被大風吹散。抖音@南昌保利天滙天坑\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/de86641be4e1bb29861c179f4805b856/2025-04/New_Project489648596.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江西南昌有屋苑的頂層「炮樓」被大風吹散。抖音@南昌保利天滙天坑\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"江西南昌有屋苑的頂層「炮樓」被大風吹散。抖音@南昌保利天滙天坑\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/75b4b76f6071dce7f58e7e707537ae34/2025-04/New_Project_1564456.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        江西南昌有屋苑的頂層「炮樓」被大風吹散。抖音@南昌保利天滙天坑\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3446725/%E5%A4%A7%E9%A2%A8%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%B9%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%B9%E5%86%A7-55%E6%AD%B2%E5%A9%A6%E9%81%AD%E5%A3%93%E6%96%83\">大風殺人︱安徽大樹被「吹冧」 55歲婦遭壓斃</a>\n</p>\n<p>有業主向媒體指，事發後居民也不敢在正常通道進出家居，怕再被崩落的磚塊砸中，只能地下停車場通道。\n\n</p>\n<p>該業主質疑，「炮樓」是偷工減料的豆腐渣工程，才會在大風吹襲下大面積崩塌。他又質疑，物管在事發後，不是保護現場取證調查，而是立即清理。這名業主又指，其單位內已裂了4處，希望政府能調查樓宇質量。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3446537/%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%A3%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%9715%E7%B4%9A%E5%A4%A7%E9%A2%A8-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3%E7%89%87%E5%90%B9%E7%94%A9%E7%AA%97%E7%B0%B7%E7%AF%B7%E4%BA%82%E9%A3%9B%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">極端天氣｜河南15級大風 網傳「災難片」：吹甩窗、簷篷亂飛｜有片</a>\n</p>\n<p>據該業主表示，「炮樓」被吹冧後，承建商方面曾解釋是設計缺陷造成，否認有偷工減料。說法不獲居民接受。\n\n</p>\n<p>涉事轄區的住建局工作人員向媒體指，已派員前去現場調查有沒有安全問題，但要等專家鑑定後才有結論。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
