            "title": "財政預算案．持續更新︱立法會恢復二讀辯論《2025年撥款條例草案》",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"立法會恢復二讀辯論《2025年撥款條例草案》\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c47b3d17c8e50ed453838641936e539f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041611291648336.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">立法會恢復二讀辯論《2025年撥款條例草案》</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><p bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:7,&quot;y&quot;:15,&quot;w&quot;:648,&quot;h&quot;:112,&quot;abs_x&quot;:94,&quot;abs_y&quot;:3015}\\'\">【財政預算案2025/立法會/陳茂波/預算案】財政司司長陳茂波2月26日宣讀新一份《財政預算案》，立法會今日（16日）起，恢復二讀《2025年撥款條例草案》辯論。今日的會議中，會由議員就該法案發言。《星島頭條》將持續更新精選發言。\n\n</p><h2 bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:7,&quot;y&quot;:5751,&quot;w&quot;:652,&quot;h&quot;:33,&quot;abs_x&quot;:94,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8454}\\'\">財政預算案2025公布時間︰</h2>\n<table bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:7,&quot;y&quot;:5803,&quot;w&quot;:499,&quot;h&quot;:166,&quot;abs_x&quot;:94,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8506}\\'\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n<tbody bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:9,&quot;y&quot;:5805,&quot;w&quot;:496,&quot;h&quot;:162,&quot;abs_x&quot;:96,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8508}\\'\">\n<tr bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:9,&quot;y&quot;:5805,&quot;w&quot;:496,&quot;h&quot;:26,&quot;abs_x&quot;:96,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8508}\\'\">\n<td bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:9,&quot;y&quot;:5805,&quot;w&quot;:139,&quot;h&quot;:26,&quot;abs_x&quot;:96,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8508}\\'\"><strong bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:11,&quot;y&quot;:5808,&quot;w&quot;:29,&quot;h&quot;:20,&quot;abs_x&quot;:98,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8511}\\'\">日期</strong></td>\n<td bis_size=\"\\'{&quot;x&quot;:150,&quot;y&quot;:5805,&quot;w&quot;:355,&quot;h&quot;:26,&quot;abs_x&quot;:237,&quot;abs_y&quot;:8508}\\'\"><strong b